OL,3,CHunt for man in attempted murder
OL,4,Cinquiry as victim fights for life in
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FDetectives investigating the attempted
OL,8,Fmurder of a man left fighting for life
OL,9,Fafter an incident in Lincoln city
OL,10,Fcentre.
OL,12,FThe victim was in a critical condition
OL,13,Fafter being found seriously injured
OL,14,Fshortly on Thursday, March 19.
OL,16,FHe was last seen walking along Lincoln
OL,17,FHigh Street with another man just
OL,18,Fafter 5.30pm, before visiting the
OL,19,FSouth Park convenience shop and
OL,20,Fcontinuing along High Street and
OL,21,FTealby Street.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
