FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1774526572
OL,3,CHunt for man in attempted murder
OL,4,Cinquiry as victim fights for life in
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FPolice believe he may also have
OL,8,Ftravelled through Sidney Street, onto
OL,9,FBargate, and then onto Craven Street.
OL,11,FCCTV has now been released showing a
OL,12,Fman walking along Lincoln High Street
OL,13,Fwho Lincolnshire Police said they want
OL,14,Fto speak to.
OL,16,FThree other men aged 31, 38 and 43
OL,17,Fhave also been arrested on suspicion
OL,18,Fof attempted murder. They remained in
OL,19,Fcustody on Tuesday.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
