OL,3,CHunt for man in attempted murder
OL,4,Cinquiry as victim fights for life in
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FThe force are appealing for any
OL,8,Fdashcam or doorbell footage which
OL,9,Fshows the same man from their footage,
OL,10,For anything suspicious for earlier
OL,11,Fthat evening and afternoon.
OL,13,FA spokesperson for Lincolnshire Police
OL,14,Fsaid: "We also urge anyone with
OL,15,Finformation that could assist our
OL,16,Finvestigation to come forward, to help
OL,17,Fus determine how he sustained his
OL,18,Finjuries.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
