OL,7,F"A 31-year-old man, a 38-year-old man,
OL,8,Fand a 43-year-old man have been
OL,9,Farrested on suspicion of attempted
OL,10,Fmurder and remain in police custody.
OL,12,F"The man remains in hospital in a
OL,13,Fcritical condition."
